    <div class="AssessmentProblem.statement"><p>A smoothie recipe calls for 3 cups of milk, 2 frozen bananas and 1 tablespoon of chocolate syrup.</p>

<ol>
	<li>Create a diagram to represent the quantities of each ingredient in the recipe.<presentation-tag data-tag-title="1 INCH" data-tree-code="MS_pi" data-tree-node-id="243962" data-tree-ref-id="215" src="/presentation_tags/4.tag"></presentation-tag>
</li>
	<li>Write 3 different sentences that use a ratio to describe the recipe.<presentation-tag data-tag-title="1 INCH" data-tree-code="MS_pi" data-tree-node-id="243962" data-tree-ref-id="215" src="/presentation_tags/4.tag"></presentation-tag>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
